b'The winning design of the Lexus Design Award 2020 GrandPrix, "Open Source Communities", is an ambitious approach to solving inequality and resource shortages through design. \xe2\x81\xa3
Lesson 1: How to safely sanitize your vehicle\xe2\x81\xa3
A) Use products with diluted, neutral detergent and water or alcohol-free type sanitizing wipes.\xe2\x81\xa3
B) Wipe interior components with a soft, damp cloth and soap (neutral detergent).\xe2\x81\xa3

b'How do you make a customer feel like a guest? When Johnny Sanacore and his wife relocated from New York to Charlotte, NC, they were seeking a fresh start. It had been several years since Johnny lost dozens of colleagues at the World Trade Center on September 11, 2001. "It was beyond friends or co-workers. It was family," Johnny says, as he reflects on those who lost their lives that day. In Charlotte, Johnny connected with the people at Hendrick Lexus Northlake and acquired his first Lexus RX. He immediately felt tied to the people there, and began visiting regularly. As Johnny says, \xe2\x80\x9cYou walk into this dealership and everybody is energetic. They have passion. They have so much fun. I just loved being here.\xe2\x80\x9d After hearing about Johnny, general manager Steve Strickland sat down with him, saw his passion for Lexus, and listened to his story. An hour later he offered him a job. Steve says, \xe2\x80\x9cHe quickly became part of our team here. It\xe2\x80\x99s a family.\xe2\x80\x9d Making employees and customers feel like family is just a part of the hospitality every Lexus dealer takes pride in providing. It\xe2\x80\x99s about listening to customers and understanding their needs. It\xe2\x80\x99s what you would do for a guest in your home. And it was all inspired by you.'
